Number Conversions (10 points)
Convert the following decimal number to binary:
1, 9, 10, 100, 624
 
Convert the following decimal numbers to hexadecimal:
10, 40, 624, 999
 
Convert the following hexadecimal numbers to decimal:
5, a, 3f, 100, bd92
